{"tid":305363,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意   吳雨霏(Kary Ng) - 座右銘  ?!?!?","createTime":"2017-07-01T15:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T17:49:38.000Z","uid":62257,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bf225137e5d05927c916efadf6da0c7963cd36","tid":305363,"uid":62257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"最近狂loop返呢首歌, 真係好鍾意<br />\n吳雨霏唔少歌都正,但係<br />\n第一句歌詞就hit中你嘅真係少見<br />\n<br />\n仲要係,原來首歌咁就過左10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xMk1Fl6iI3w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxMk1Fl6iI3w&d=AOliCmYgTrQQCVNHzCrRPBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e63eb685\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xMk1Fl6iI3w</a><br />\n作曲：Walter Wong       填詞：方杰<br />\n很信命　當我每次哭　亦只有結他聲<br />\n喃喃自語數星星　孤單也像註定<br />\n祈求被愛的溫馨　呼天都不應　已經很適應<br />\n我心事　誰又會在意想聽<br />\n<br />\n很冷靜　知道我愛的　定把我當佈景<br />\n平凡像我這一種　今天要認了命<br />\n才能學會不貪心　碰不到戀愛　也毫無反應<br />\n單戀相戀失戀　說穿了盡是陷阱<br />\n放手　得我有這本領<br />\n<br />\n＊一個自愛也好　越對我好<br />\n　越需要控制我反應<br />\n　對未來沒信心　怎張開眼睛<br />\n　花花世界太過美　哪有我蹤影<br />\n　怕有天放心後　才給我最愛拋棄<br />\n　我要謹守我座右銘＊<br />\n<br />\n很信命　不信有美好　幸福過更冷清<br />\n同情沒法把不安驅走　已是確定<br />\n原來避免輸不起　退出的方法　叫遺忘本性<br />\n不甘不忍不想　我只有越坐越靜<br />\n我的　快樂就像泡影<br />\n<br />\nREPEAT＊<br />\n<br />\n派對滿佈愛情來臨的風景<br />\n獨自妒忌別人　誰能夠高興<br />\n註定無人來示愛　我都不作聲<br />\n<br />\n即使一個自愛也好　越對我好<br />\n越需要控制我反應<br />\n對未來還沒信心　怎張開眼睛<br />\n花花世界太過美　哪有我蹤影<br />\n有更心跳選擇　而比我遠遠優勝<br />\n如何專一都想轉性<br />\n與情人齊眉白髮　問誰可保證﻿"},{"pid":"64ee5d5c7297bf888d4d6ee0a5fdbeae805c6eec","tid":305363,"uid":62257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"原來咁就10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48daee57c6b68ff0c7cda558afad39a237582f12","tid":305363,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a17677449f111cee69c75a25e9023c2d4ae8445","tid":305363,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b203ccdbd006477c98779578a7d6eeb7a485c3a","tid":305363,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af34f784b43e765f62f544f0eafd8e89de7248b3","tid":305363,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d85f18f4976da491e063e69c602de95685cb1d","tid":305363,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n仲有好多歌都好正呀<br />\n二十世紀少年<br />\n吳哥窟<br />\n<br />\n越數越多，唔數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8682769a22250cfe00cb3398df95a54b32defb","tid":305363,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4b0726ad87e6ee734788fffb9afeb7450dd5e7","tid":305363,"uid":15182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"生命樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acbc59e53e368f7dd3b6e4902962d55a09799b5","tid":305363,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T22:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cla